## Verification Checklist

After deployment, verify each component renders correctly:

1. CTA Button - displays with proper styling
1. Feature Grid - shows 3 features in columns
1. Content Card - has border, icon, and title
1. Stats - shows numbers prominently
1. Colored Section - has green background
1. Content Box - has visible border
1. FAQ Accordion - items expand/collapse
1. YouTube - video embed loads
1. Testimonial - quote and attribution styled
1. Two Columns - side-by-side on desktop
1. Donate Button - styled with icon
1. Image Section - image with overlay visible

Testing
